= Lepra2

Lepra2 is the second generation database for tracking patients with
leprosy. Lepra2 is designed for Ruby on Rails 3.1. The SQL server is
MySQL.

== Install and run

Requirements (Debian Sid):

  apt-get install libmysqlclient-dev libopenssl apache2 coffeescript nodejs
  
Ruby 1.9.2 gems:

  gem install mysql2
  gem install rails

Run (you probably want to use rvm)

  rvm use 1.9.2
  rails server
 
